How...how's your wound?

879
00:38:05,870 --> 00:38:06,600
She's fine.

880
00:38:07,600 --> 00:38:08,390
The arrow didn't go deep,

881
00:38:08,390 --> 00:38:09,360
so it didn't hurt the bones.

882
00:38:09,520 --> 00:38:10,320
I've taken care of it.

883
00:38:15,800 --> 00:38:16,870
Are you done treating?

884
00:38:17,430 --> 00:38:18,280
I'm done.

885
00:38:24,870 --> 00:38:26,120
I've finished.

886
00:38:31,360 --> 00:38:32,120
I'll just leave.

887
00:38:32,870 --> 00:38:33,520
Your Honor.

888
00:38:33,520 --> 00:38:33,910
Okay.

889
00:38:46,760 --> 00:38:47,560
Don't stand up.

890
00:38:51,950 --> 00:38:52,760
Forgot to close the door.

891
00:38:52,840 --> 00:38:54,230
Please go on.

892
00:39:04,470 --> 00:39:05,080
What's this?

893
00:39:06,080 --> 00:39:06,870
It's ginger decoction.

894
00:39:06,870 --> 00:39:07,950
Drink it while it's hot.

895
00:39:08,910 --> 00:39:09,870
It'll warm you up.

896
00:39:11,040 --> 00:39:12,000
Thanks, Your Honor.

897
00:39:17,800 --> 00:39:19,670
If it doesn't taste good,
please forgive me.

898
00:39:20,950 --> 00:39:22,150
Why?

899
00:39:24,950 --> 00:39:27,320
I cooked it myself.

900
00:39:28,670 --> 00:39:29,760
I'm afraid you may catch a cold.

901
00:39:29,870 --> 00:39:30,670
I intended to ask Baozi

902
00:39:30,670 --> 00:39:31,760
to make it and send it over.

903
00:39:32,190 --> 00:39:32,910
But when I went to the kitchen,

904
00:39:32,910 --> 00:39:34,360
I remembered that she had a day off.

905
00:39:34,390 --> 00:39:35,760
So,

906
00:39:36,080 --> 00:39:37,320
I cooked it myself.

907
00:39:44,800 --> 00:39:45,950
How does it taste?

908
00:39:56,120 --> 00:39:56,870
I regret

909
00:39:56,870 --> 00:39:58,150
having you work at the county yamen.

910
00:39:59,230 --> 00:40:00,560
It was so dangerous today.

911
00:40:01,190 --> 00:40:02,840
If Mr. Qi didn't happen to be there,

912
00:40:02,840 --> 00:40:04,280
I can't imagine the consequence.

913
00:40:05,230 --> 00:40:06,560
I like being a constable

914
00:40:06,870 --> 00:40:08,280
and working at the county yamen.

915
00:40:08,870 --> 00:40:10,080
I'm so grateful

916
00:40:10,360 --> 00:40:11,670
that you allow me to work here.

917
00:40:11,670 --> 00:40:13,080
But I don't want you to take risks.

918
00:40:13,870 --> 00:40:14,600
I don't want you

919
00:40:14,600 --> 00:40:16,000
to get hurt.

920
00:40:17,000 --> 00:40:17,870
Promise me,

921
00:40:18,600 --> 00:40:19,840
if you're in danger in the future,

922
00:40:19,840 --> 00:40:21,560
don't rush in alone.

923
00:40:21,950 --> 00:40:24,000
I know you're brave and smart.

924
00:40:24,230 --> 00:40:25,080
But in my heart,

925
00:40:25,080 --> 00:40:26,190
you should be protected by me,

926
00:40:26,190 --> 00:40:28,040
not charging ahead for me.

927
00:40:31,280 --> 00:40:32,080
Luo Shu.

928
00:40:39,950 --> 00:40:40,760
Come in.

929
00:40:43,320 --> 00:40:44,120
Your Honor.

930
00:40:44,280 --> 00:40:45,280
Have you found Qiao Ruolan?

931
00:40:45,520 --> 00:40:46,280
No.

932
00:40:46,390 --> 00:40:47,150
I've told Wu Er

933
00:40:47,150 --> 00:40:47,950
to send more people to look for her.

934
00:40:48,950 --> 00:40:49,560
Okay.

935
00:40:49,870 --> 00:40:51,320
It's ready for you to interrogate.

936
00:40:52,800 --> 00:40:53,320
Let's go.

937
00:40:53,470 --> 00:40:54,040
Got it.

938
00:41:00,950 --> 00:41:01,870
Get some rest.

939
00:41:45,190 --> 00:41:46,710
Young Master.

940
00:41:46,710 --> 00:41:47,870
Why did you spend ten liang

941
00:41:47,870 --> 00:41:48,950
at the Deyilou Resturant

942
00:41:48,950 --> 00:41:50,600
just for this bowl of ginger decoction?

943
00:41:50,760 --> 00:41:51,630
You don't understand.

944
00:41:51,630 --> 00:41:52,390
Give it to me.

945
00:41:52,760 --> 00:41:53,710
You can go back.

946
00:41:53,710 --> 00:41:54,560
Don't follow me.

947
00:41:55,520 --> 00:41:56,320
Miss Luo,

948
00:41:57,670 --> 00:41:58,470
I'm coming in.

949
00:42:02,760 --> 00:42:03,600
What are you drinking?

950
00:42:04,710 --> 00:42:05,390
Ginger decoction.

951
00:42:06,390 --> 00:42:07,560
I also get you ginger decoction

952
00:42:09,710 --> 00:42:10,520
and chicken soup.

953
00:42:21,390 --> 00:42:22,190
Today,

954
00:42:22,560 --> 00:42:24,390
thank you for saving my life.

955
00:42:26,190 --> 00:42:27,320
Come on.

956
00:42:27,360 --> 00:42:28,190
I'm a man.

957
00:42:28,230 --> 00:42:29,520
I just uphold justice.

958
00:42:40,190 --> 00:42:41,320
It doesn't taste good.

959
00:42:41,600 --> 00:42:42,230
Drink mine.

960
00:42:43,520 --> 00:42:44,520
It's okay, Mr. Qi.

961
00:42:44,520 --> 00:42:45,520
I'll just drink this.

962
00:42:45,760 --> 00:42:46,600
Drink mine. Trust me.

963
00:42:46,600 --> 00:42:47,390
I'm fine.

964
00:42:47,430 --> 00:42:48,000
Drink mine.

965
00:42:48,000 --> 00:42:48,360
Trust me.

966
00:43:08,420 --> 00:43:12,420
Who dances alone under the moon?

967
00:43:12,540 --> 00:43:16,380
Stubbornly breaking free from chains

968
00:43:16,820 --> 00:43:20,300
Who lives a life with clever plans?

969
00:43:20,460 --> 00:43:24,220
Chasing in the sound of hooves

970
00:43:25,140 --> 00:43:28,940
A restless soul

971
00:43:29,220 --> 00:43:32,940
Breaking out of the cage and flying

972
00:43:33,260 --> 00:43:35,500
Listening to the wind, so mysterious

973
00:43:35,740 --> 00:43:37,580
The moon shines on my troubles

974
00:43:37,740 --> 00:43:40,740
This journey matters because of you

975
00:43:41,700 --> 00:43:43,860
The judge of fate

976
00:43:44,140 --> 00:43:45,780
Can't change my resolve

977
00:43:46,180 --> 00:43:49,620
Even if the ink dries

978
00:43:50,340 --> 00:43:52,500
Heaven overlooks all

979
00:43:52,660 --> 00:43:54,540
Earth tallies the hours

980
00:43:54,660 --> 00:43:57,700
I long for you to be by my side

981
00:43:58,620 --> 00:44:00,780
Clearly missing you

982
00:44:01,060 --> 00:44:02,780
The past is all scattered

983
00:44:03,140 --> 00:44:06,620
You are my bright moon

984
00:44:17,220 --> 00:44:21,180
Who dances alone under the moon?

985
00:44:21,300 --> 00:44:25,260
Stubbornly breaking free from chains

986
00:44:25,580 --> 00:44:29,060
Who's drumming at the door?

987
00:44:29,260 --> 00:44:33,020
Waking the dust from dreams

988
00:44:33,900 --> 00:44:37,740
A restless soul

989
00:44:38,060 --> 00:44:41,620
Breaking out of the cage and flying

990
00:44:42,060 --> 00:44:44,340
Hearing the wind, secrets unfold

991
00:44:44,420 --> 00:44:46,340
The moon shines into my dreams

992
00:44:46,460 --> 00:44:49,460
This journey is enough with you here

993
00:44:50,420 --> 00:44:52,660
It's unrelated to fate's details

994
00:44:52,780 --> 00:44:54,740
Just because I never gave up

995
00:44:54,820 --> 00:44:58,380
Even with many thorns

996
00:44:58,780 --> 00:45:01,140
The heavens won't let me down

997
00:45:01,220 --> 00:45:03,180
The earth helps me seek

998
00:45:03,260 --> 00:45:06,220
Eventually, the clouds will clear

999
00:45:07,220 --> 00:45:09,340
In this gentle and simple world

1000
00:45:09,660 --> 00:45:11,500
Laugh through partings and reunions

1001
00:45:11,660 --> 00:45:17,580
My heart only follows the moon
